About 5 years ago I installed a rebuilt engine from a reputable rebuilder. 
It ran like cr*p and failed after less than 5000 miles...

So, if you do not want to build your engine yourself find someone you trust 
to do it for you.  It will cost more but you will have what you want.

Cheers,

